{"tid":1279078,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【8ch香港版版主】頭先8ch同4chan都死咗","createTime":"2019-07-02T14:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T16:13:54.000Z","uid":131691,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bb68283d1470bba810a04f60625c352a30a0d45e","tid":1279078,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係普通一個香港人，亦都係8ch香港版嘅版主<br />\n原本想開個8ch做後備，當初最主要原因係條濕鳩「不誠實取用電腦」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係今日8ch同連登一齊死，因為攻擊對象係Cloudflare<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基本上中共如果真心想係咁攻擊cloudflare，我諗熄燈嘅時間可以好長<br />\n同時間有好多通訊platform會死：lihkg, hkgolden, discord, 8ch, 4chan, ptt, 仲有好似立場都死，香討好似都有事<br />\n<br />\n所以如果中共真係想打，而家大家真係要搵定backup嘅通訊方法，telegram無事，wire無事，reddit無事，whatsapp無事，signal無事。<br />\n<br />\n當然，reddit嗰個騰訊股份... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想用Firechat / Briar玩mesh network communication嘅，麻煩而家register定個account，到時出事就冇得register㗎啦"},{"pid":"c9706ac5a845fa088d9bd6a1ab24c57af6d6faa9","tid":1279078,"uid":219211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90378c2814c5160037bb5bb8b2e5f61e57c88ed0","tid":1279078,"uid":131691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後提醒一句：<br />\n千祈唔好幾個論壇/溝通平台用同一個username，同一個password</span>"},{"pid":"f09904557857c1c5ace74845f8fd2fce5cbd70ec","tid":1279078,"uid":3083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:53:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa7d1fcd705765be5d6aaa220e89532609440602","tid":1279078,"uid":26161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"推 點都要有幾條後備既路線for溝通"},{"pid":"88598cda3038650980bfe5e0349d77db