&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;<br />\nCloudflare 是否會提供中文版的服務？<br />\nCloudflare 並不會提供中文版服務，但我們的合作夥伴「百度」會提供我們服務的當地語系化版本，稱為「百度雲加速」。百度雲加速所提供的功能和 Cloudflare 相同 (CDN、DNS、DDoS 防護、WAF 等)，但卻是為中國市場所量身打造。如需詳細資訊，請瀏覽 <a href=\"http://su.baidu.com/。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsu.baidu.com%2F%E3%80%82&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRczaf%2B7McJKZiP%2F5rhSwlYLA%3D&h=e19a52e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://su.baidu.com/。</a><br />\n<br />\n如果您已是 Cloudflare 客戶，希望轉換到百度雲加速的簡體中文平台，我們的知識庫中有篇關於該選擇 Cloudflare 還是百度雲加速的文章，歡迎您前往閱讀其中的詳細資訊。請注意，一個網域不能同時在 Cloudflare 和百度雲加速上啟用。<br />\n&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;"},{"pid":"cbcc399ad4c95cefd502e71fcdd560d51a957e6f","tid":1279078,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:00:13.000Z","msg":"（方舟）［出事嗰陣用］<a href=\"http://Hack.chat/?hongkonger\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHack.chat%2F%3Fhongkonger&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRczaf%2B7McJKZiP%2F5rhSwlYLA%3D&h=732e291c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://Hack.chat/?hongkonger</a><br />\n<br />\n[安全上網]Hack.chat匿名文字通訊聊天室使用教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1226389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1226389</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"43126890d019c7fd210ebdfea8beeb099deba882","tid":1279078,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:00:31.000Z","msg":"hexchat<br />\n自動篩走低IQ人士"},{"pid":"f4ee41fc09fb9c6ff58de0073409a33262d2b4c1","tid":1279078,"uid":216513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cbcc399ad4c95cefd502e71fcdd560d51a957e6f","tid":1279078,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re